text: int main ( ) { int i , n1 , n2 , y1 , y2 , l , t , x = 1 ; scanf ( "%d" , & t ) ; while ( t -- ) { x = 1 ; scanf ( "%d%d" , & n1 , & n2 ) ; y1 = n1 ; y2 = n2 ; if ( n1 < n2 ) { while ( x != 0 ) { x = n2 % n1 ; n2 = n1 ; n1 = x ; } printf ( "%d " , n2 ) ; l = y1 * y2 / n2 ; printf ( "%d\n" , l ) ; } else { while ( x != 0 ) { x = n1 % n2 ; n1 = n2 ; n2 = x ; } printf ( "%d " , n1 ) ; l = y1 * y2 / n1 ; printf ( "%d\n" , l ) ; } } return 0 ; }
